premise_source_doc_sentence: It was released worldwide on September 9 , 2014 , for the PlayStation 3 , PlayStation 4 , Xbox 360 , and Xbox One consoles .
It was GamesRadar 's 2014 Game of the Year and it received the BAFTA Award for Best Game at the 2014 British Academy Video Games Awards .
There are four pieces of downloadable content  (  DLC  )  that were released for Bungie 's 2014 first-person shooter video game Destiny .

Released on September 15 , 2015 , as the third expansion of Destiny , it revolves around Oryx , The Taken King and his plot for revenge after players slew his son Crota in Destinys first downloadable content  (  DLC  )  pack , The Dark Below .
A third , larger expansion , The Taken King , was released in September 2015 and marked the beginning of Year Two , changing much of the core gameplay .
